  "title": "Logistics Crew @ Jurong",
  "description": "<h2>Warehouse Operations Assistant (Logistics Crew) @Jurong</h2><p><strong>Salary:</strong> <strong>$2,500 – $3,000/month</strong><br /><strong>Location:</strong> <strong>Jurong</strong></p><h3>Daily Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Pick, pack, and prepare orders accurately</p></li><li><p>Receive and check incoming stock deliveries</p></li><li><p>Sort, label, and arrange items neatly in the warehouse</p></li><li><p>Load/unload goods and assist with simple warehouse movement</p></li><li><p>Support stock count and basic inventory checking</p></li><li><p>Keep the workspace clean, safe, and well-organized</p></li><li><p>Work closely with the team to meet daily targets</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Comfortable with physical work (standing, lifting, moving items)</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
